9. f3
9. Ne5 {Here we go. Our queenside pawns are about to march.} 
10. Bb3 {Or10.Be2c6. The pawns are still coming.} 
10. a5 {It turns out the bishop is rather short on squares. See the main chapter for a deeper examination of this position.} 
