16. Ng5 {Pichot's choice against me.16.Nbd2Kh8would once again leave us with a clear extra tempo over11.Be3.} 
16. Kh8 {16...b6?Unfortunately, it being blitz, I blundered against Pichot in 2022.17.Bb3+Kh818.Bf7!Oops! White blocks our defense of the h5-knight. It wouldn't be so bad, but after Qxh5, White will also threaten mate. I managed to last over 100 moves, but Black is objectively lost. Don't fall for this trick!This sidestep would have prevented any problems. With ...Rd8 and ...Qg6, we already have a clear advantage.} 
17. Bb3
17. Qg6 {White had just set up the same trick again with Bf7. Please don't allow it! Now the queen safely guards our knight. White can exchange our d7-bishop for the g5-knight, but we have a huge attack.} 
