14. Bxe4 {The more natural recapture. This was essayed in a correspondence game from 2021.} 
14. Qf7 {Our queen is a bit precarious on the e-file so let's move it. Apart from the immediate hit on the c4-knight, we also have ideas of capturing twice on d4 to open the f-file.} 
15. Ne3 {The natural retreat, but White has to be careful now.} 
15. exd4 {We exploit the pressure down the f-file,15...Nf4!?is also fine.} 
16. cxd4
16. Nxd4 {Our tactical shot. Taking the knight is impossible.} 
17. Nxd4
17. Qxf2+ {Once the king goes to h1, either immediately or after18.Kh2Be5+, we'llhave ...Ng3+ collecting the bishop on e4.} 
