13. Bxg5
14. Nxg5
14. Nd7 {Stijve-Wagner, Bad Ragaz 2019. We might be suffering a bit, but as it is White has no way to seize the initiative. White should probably take on d7 here. If they don't, they're likely to suffer with their worse bishop.} 
