8. O-O {Now castling will transpose to7.O-OBg78.Be3O-O, analyzed shortly.} 
9. Nbd2 {White's argument is they want to develop the knight to g3 before castling, so the f1-square is available. We've seen the idea backfire before, but this time White has at least been able to develop their bishop.} 
