14. f6
15. Bxf6 {Once again, the knight will simply be trapped if White captures on c8. We just take the bishop.} 
15. gxf6 {Our king looks a little vulnerable, but White has yet to develop their queenside and can't create any threats. We're just an exchange up.} 
