9. h3 {With our king on g8, we're less likely to advance our g-pawn.} 
9. h6 {We're ready to challenge White with ...Be6. Starting with9...Be6is possible, but10.Bc2is a bit annoying. White will manage toplay d3-d4 before we're absolutely ready for ...d6-d5. Now we won't have to worry about Ng5 ideas.} 
