6. Qe7+ {A strong recommendation from Martin Lokander. White doesn't have a good way to parry the check.} 
7. Qe2 {The queen exchange won't suffice.} 
7. Nb4 {We threaten both ...Nxc2+ and collect the d-pawn. White cannot defend both.} 
8. Na3
8. Nfxd5 {A clear extra pawn.} 
