7. Qe2+ {White has also tried7.O-Obut has nothing like enough compensation after either recaptureon f6. Magnus chose the pawn in a blitz game with MVL, but7...Qxf6is probably even stronger.} 
7. Be6 {Safely guarding everything. White is already lost.} 
