11. f6 {But we don't need to oblige.} 
12. a3 {Wesley played12...a5here, which is fine, but with White putting pressure on the kingside I'd prefer another possibility.} 
12. O-O-O {Our king is going to be perfectly safe on b8. We'll turn the tables and attack on the kingside instead.} 
