8. Ne5 {The strong idea. Since White gave us a pawn on move two we've repaid the debt with interest, returning two pawns and a rook. But White's monarchs are now both in trouble. The threat is to capture twice on f3. Then we'll have a skewer with ...Qh5+ collecting White's queen.} 
